title: NBA Finals Game 6 Preview | Real Ones
description:
Logan is joined by Rob Mahoney to discuss what they’re looking for in Game 6, whether this is a legacy-defining game for Jayson Tatum, and how the Warriors’ depth has played in the series so far.
Host: Logan Murdock
Guest: Rob Mahoney
Associate Producer: Carlos Chiriboga
